Text:
1. Harusnya pada awal-awal penemuan dulu akan lebih baik jika penemuan NIKUBA ditanggapi secara positif terlebih dahulu oleh pihak-pihak terkait di negeri ini (BRIN, Kemendikbudristek, dll)
2. Undang penemu NIKUBA untuk mempresentasikan;
3. Jika memungkinkan dikembangkan ya didukung untuk riset lebih lanjut untuk disempurnakan, apalagi penemu NIKUBA bukanlah seorang peneliti yang berlatar belakang akademisi yang mana penelitiannya mungkin tidak sesuai dengan SOP penelitian di kampus, sedangkan pihak BR!N dan kampus melihatnya dari sudut SOP penelitian akademis; Ingat bahwa banyak penemuan2 besar di dunia yang tidak ada background kampus dari penemunya, tetapi hasil dari trial and error yang berkali2 bahkan ratusan atau ribuan coba-coba dan hasil penemuannya bisa kita rasakan sama saat ini;
4. Jika ada sinergi antara penemu NIKUBA dengan pihak BRIN akan sangat bagus, penemu NIKUBA bisa terus melakukan penelitiannya, sedangkan pihak BRIN bisa meluruskan prosedeur risetnya;
5. Apapun yang dilakukan oleh anak bangsa terkait inovasi harus dihargai apalagi untuk kepentingan orang banyak. Jangan langsung dicibir, dicaci, dan dikritisi habis2an.

TextEng:
1. In the early days of the discovery, it would have been better if the discovery of NIKUBA had been responded positively by the relevant parties in this country (National Agency for Research and Innovation, Ministry of Education and Culture, etc.)
2. Invite NIKUBA inventors to present;
3. If it is possible to develop it, it is supported for further research to be perfected, especially since the inventor of NIKUBA is not a researcher with an academic background, where his research may not be in accordance with the research SOPs on campus, while BR!N and the campus look at it from the point of view of academic research SOPs; Remember that there are many great discoveries in the world that did not have a campus background from their inventors, but were the result of repeated trials and errors, even hundreds or thousands of trials and we can feel the results of the findings today;
4. If there is a synergy between the inventors of NIKUBA and the BRIN, it will be very good, the inventors of NIKUBA can continue to carry out their research, while the BRIN can straighten out the research procedures;
5. Whatever is done by the nation's children regarding innovation must be appreciated, especially for the benefit of the people. Don't be immediately scorned, insulted, and criticized all over.
